org.apache.jena.sparql.syntax.syntaxtransform

Class ElementTransformer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.jena.sparql.syntax.syntaxtransform.ElementTransformer

  • public class ElementTransformer
extends Object
    A bottom-up application of a transformation of SPARQL syntax Elements. QueryTransformOps.transform(org.apache.jena.query.Query, java.util.Map<org.apache.jena.sparql.core.Var, org.apache.jena.graph.Node>) provides the mechanism to apply to a Query.
    See Also:
    ElementTransformCopyBase, UpdateTransformOps.transform(org.apache.jena.update.Update, java.util.Map<org.apache.jena.sparql.core.Var, org.apache.jena.graph.Node>)
